strings: <voice_0x0100173D><se_high>Media princess: My wedding was planned a long time ago by both families. I guess I have no other choice than to accept it.
<voice_0x0100173E><se_high>Media princess: I will always protect you I think it's my princess' duty...
<voice_0x0100173F><se_high>Media princess: I can't afford it! If I had to choose between marrying an idiot or finding out the truth, I would make myself a sandwich!
<voice_0x01001740><se_high>Media princess: I cannot live to have my honesty rejected!
<voice_0x01001741><se_high>Media princess: Hold my hand and let's run together! <hero> Get me out of here!
